acquired.name: Veeral Controls
acquired.short_description: Veeral Controls manufactures power supplies, wind energy systems, drives, and power controllers.
acquired.description: We are a 40 year old company registered under ISO 9001:2008, engaging in manufacturing of latest technology for power and electrical solutions. Our innovation extends across Wind Energy, Solar Energy, Renewable energy and General power solutions. Our team comprises of the most efficient and talented staff in design, engineering, production and administration which has always resulted in delivery of the highest quality products and on time. For us, client satisfaction has been the utmost priority with serving national and international clients like Regen Powertech, ABB, Institute for Plasma Research (IPR), Bharat Heavy Electricals Ltd, Gujarat Electricity Corporation, Johnson Screen India ltd, Rockwell Automation India and many more.
acquired.descriptionShort: Veeral Controls manufactures power supplies, wind energy systems, drives, and power controllers.

acquired.name: Hyperion Accounting Group
acquired.short_description: Hyperion Accounting Group provides expert tax, audit, and financial planning services for businesses and individuals.
acquired.description: Hyperion Accounting Group, founded in 2025 by David C. Papotta, CPA, offers comprehensive accounting and financial solutions tailored to individuals and businesses. With over 25 years of experience, the firm specializes in tax preparation, audit assistance, balance financial records, and financial planning, serving a diverse range of industries including agriculture, aviation, construction, and real estate. Their approach emphasizes collaboration, accuracy, and strategic guidance to help clients achieve their financial and operational goals, with a focus on providing solutions for tax savings, audit needs, and estate planning.

acquired.name: Williamson Insurance
acquired.short_description: Williamson Insurance offers tailored insurance and risk management solutions for businesses and individuals.
acquired.description: Williamson Insurance is an independent insurance agency with over 50 years of experience providing tailored insurance and risk management solutions for businesses and individuals. They partner with numerous insurance carriers to offer a wide range of financial protection plans, acting as advocates for their clients. The company emphasizes expertise, integrity, and superior customer service, aiming to exceed client expectations. Their services include a comprehensive suite of business insurance options such as property, general liability, cyber security, and commercial auto, as well as personal insurance for life, home, car, and boat.

acquired.name: Northern Insurance Service
acquired.short_description: Northern Insurance offers a wide range of insurance solutions for individuals and businesses.
acquired.description: Northern Insurance is a diversified, full-service insurance agency founded in 2005, building on the legacy of Cornolo Insurance Agency established in 1927. They serve individuals and businesses across the U.S. and beyond, with a strong focus on providing sound advice and excellent customer service. Northern Insurance offers a wide range of insurance solutions, including Business, Home, Auto, Toy, Health, and Life Insurance. Their business model emphasizes personalized consultations with experienced agents to ensure clients understand their options and receive timely assistance. They are committed to helping clients focus on what matters by providing comprehensive protection and support through tailored insurance policies, aiming to be a trusted advisor in every aspect of their clients' lives.

acquired.name: Cabel Industry
acquired.short_description: Cabel provides IT solutions and services for the banking and financial sectors.
acquired.description: Cabel is an ICT Service Provider established in 1985, specializing in the development and distribution of integrated banking IT solutions. The company offers a comprehensive range of services across ICT, professional services, and financial services, supported by a network of eleven companies. Cabel focuses on developing high-tech services for the banking sector with a strong emphasis on ethical conduct, customer interests, community, and environmental protection. Their commitment to continuous pursuit of excellence, high quality standards, productivity, and technological innovation makes them a reliable, efficient, and transparent partner. Cabel's core business is built on a solid financial foundation and advanced know-how, allowing them to transform market needs into innovative solutions, providing clients with benefits such as access to skilled professionals, scalable solutions, reduced operational costs, and adherence to strict SLAs and KPIs. Cabel is part of the Quid Group.
acquired.descriptionShort: Cabel provides IT solutions and services for the banking and financial sectors.
